Data Availability Statement
All data generated or analyzed during this study are included in this published article and its Supplementary Information Files. The MS/MS raw data and analysis have been deposited in the ProteomeXchange Consortium via the jPOST partner repository with the data set identifier JPST002506 and PXD049309 (https://proteomecentral.proteomexchange.org/cgi/GetDataset?ID=PXD049309, accessed on 29 July 2024).
